{"tid":1116433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果唔係安心事件 我都唔會咁得閒走去聽老鼠安啲歌","createTime":"2019-04-20T03:54:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T04:37:24.000Z","uid":18581,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b99ef5140a88289087d6f97601b7111f6f53cbd6","tid":1116433,"uid":18581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:54:23.000Z","msg":"平時聽廣東歌 都係聽啲大路嘢<br />\n陳奕迅 張敬軒 古巨基呢啲<br />\n因為呢一件事諗住聽下佢啲歌笑下佢<br />\n唯獨你是不可取替 呢啲歌完全違背咗現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實佢有啲歌都好聽 細個聽過但係唔記得<br />\n唔係剩係得一首流淚行勝利道嘅<br />\n<br />\n睇隔離po話佢生不逢時 遇着四大天王<br />\n先搞到紅唔起 就唔知la<br />\n不過安心事件的確係令佢紅咗<br />\n至少我走咗去聽佢啲歌笑9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4f40f7b81bd46931ccdf092edfdcff10cf513f","tid":1116433,"uid":159444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"佢有d歌係ok嘅，但佢唱真係唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce7627c38468611f04811268743eb57664cfa48","tid":1116433,"uid":18581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af4f40f7b81bd46931ccdf092edfdcff10cf513f","tid":1116433,"uid":159444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T03:57:38.000Z","msg":"佢有d歌係ok嘅，但佢唱真係唔ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"的確係 我覺得係啲歌詞好正囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c196edce70b4795f6f011579d9a6455bbdbcc1d","tid":1116433,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"鼻音<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4f8b572a2d5ef2bdd28976aae90a58c1ec3114","tid":1116433,"uid":248021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:21:01.000Z","msg":"唔覺得佢啲情歌無晒靈魂 <br />\n好丟臉 好嘔心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f